The following TLA+ tools are available in this distribution:

 1) The Syntactic Analyzer: A parser and syntax checker for TLA+2
    specifications.

 2) TLC2: A model checker and simulator for a subclass of "executable"
    TLA+2 specifications.

 3) TLATeX: A program for typesetting TLA+ specifications.   

 4) The PlusCal translator

For instruction to install and run the tools, please go to

   http://research.microsoft.com/users/lamport/tla/tools.html
